  <summary date="2019-08-29T19:35:35Z" status="Introduced in House">Voting Innovation Prize Act of 2018

This bill directs the Election Assistance Commission to (1) identify elements in voting systems most in need of innovation, and (2) conduct an annual prize competition to encourage the development of technologies to address such elements.</summary>
